login

As a user, I want to be able to create a username and password combo so that I can log into the chat application.
As a user, I want to be able to put in my username and password and be sent to the chat screen of my choice.
As a user, I want to have a button that will allow me to reset my password in case I forget it.
As a user, I want to be able to sign in with Facebook so that I don't need to remember another username password combo.

Registration/Login
As a user, I want to be able to create a username, password, and email combo so that I can log into the chat application.
As a user, I want to be able to put in my username and password and be sent to the chat screen of my choice.
As a user, I want to have a button that will allow me to reset my password via email in case I forget it.

--login--
As a user I want to be able to insert a username and password to log in to the application
As a user I want to be able to create a username and password to log in to the application
As a user I want to be able to insert my email in the Registration process so if i forget my password i have a place for them to be sent
As a user I want to be able to edit my password or have a forget my password if I need a new password

CHANNEL:
As a user, I want to see multiple channels so that I can differentiate topics.
As a user, I want to be able to create a new channel or hide channel so I can only see the channels I want.
As a user, I want to rename the channel.
As a user, I want to prioritize the channels.
As a user, I want to see who is in the channel.

PROFILE:
As a user, I want to be able to edit/update my information.
As a user, I want to be able to upload a profile picture.

MESSAGING:
As a user, I want to be able to send messages to  multiply people or a single person or to the channel.

Chat Window:
As a user, I want to display all the messages
As a user, I want to be able to create a message
As a user, I want to see who wrote and sent the message